 <summary>Application for adding watermarks to images</summary>
 <description>
  <p>
   Watermark is an easy-to-use application that allows users to add custom watermarks to their images.
   It supports various image formats and provides expert options to customize the watermark text and appearance.
  </p>
 </description>
