   <description>
    <p>Main features</p>
    <ul>
     <li>Add watermarks to multiple images</li>
     <li>Can export to PDF or JPG files</li>
     <li>Expert mode: font selection, font color choice or random, font transparency,
     text angle, watermark density, optional Date + Hour, filename prefix, PDF or JPG output,
     JPG compression level, image resize</li>
